  "title": "FEAT: Implement Natural Nation Day 1 Member-Facing Foundation with Founder Corrections",
  "summary": "This pull request introduces the initial member-facing frontend foundation for Natural Nation, located under `app/frontend`. It includes core UI components, basic styling, and essential setup files. All five founder-requested corrections have been applied, addressing UI text, styling, feature placeholders, performance meta tags, and accessibility attributes.",
